WEBVTT

00:01.150 --> 00:02.870
Previously on damages...

00:02.910 --> 00:05.430
The bureau's putting together
a case we'll want patty to take.

00:05.460 --> 00:07.470
We'll use you to monitor
it from the inside.

00:07.490 --> 00:10.090
What is patty's interest in this murder?

00:10.100 --> 00:12.090
I think daniel purcell
and her are friends.

00:12.110 --> 00:14.120
- Well,this is not what we wanted.
- I know.

00:14.310 --> 00:15.690
You owe me.

00:15.710 --> 00:17.450
I owe you nothing.

00:17.470 --> 00:20.700
I'm advising mr. Purcell not
to answer any more questions.

00:20.730 --> 00:22.160
I thought you said you
weren't his attorney.

00:22.170 --> 00:23.230
I am now.

00:23.240 --> 00:25.650
You were found with your wife's body.

00:25.690 --> 00:27.810
There's no sign of forced entry.

00:27.830 --> 00:29.580
Patty,I saw the guy who did it.

00:29.590 --> 00:34.480
Our firm was hired to do toxicity
studies on a chemical compound--

00:34.490 --> 00:35.540
aracite.

00:35.550 --> 00:36.380
Is it toxic?

00:36.400 --> 00:37.370
Extremely.

00:37.400 --> 00:40.630
Do you think your firm killed christine?

00:40.660 --> 00:42.710
They consult for the energy industry.

00:42.740 --> 00:46.380
These companies are
worth billions of dollars.

00:46.410 --> 00:48.730
Hey,mom. You okay?

00:48.740 --> 00:50.590
Michael,this is daniel purcell.

00:50.620 --> 00:51.660
It's good to meet you.

00:51.670 --> 00:54.480
We have a containment problem.

00:54.520 --> 00:56.600
By all means,share.

00:56.620 --> 00:58.070
Claire maddox--
I've heard of her.

00:58.090 --> 01:01.580
She's head counsel of the world's
third largest energy provider.

01:01.610 --> 01:04.480
- Did you tell anyone about us?
- No.

01:11.560 --> 01:14.230
Did you kill your wife?

01:17.150 --> 01:20.610
I had nothing to do with this.

01:22.660 --> 01:25.180
did she find out about us?

01:31.370 --> 01:33.450
No.

01:37.150 --> 01:41.370
Someone leaked your toxicity
report to patty hewes.

01:43.610 --> 01:45.830
I did.

01:46.630 --> 01:48.640
Why?

01:48.650 --> 01:52.100
There are some things I
don't want you to know.

01:52.110 --> 01:55.120
For your protection.

01:55.560 --> 01:58.790
You have got to tell me the truth.

01:59.630 --> 02:02.860
Who is responsible for this?

02:03.960 --> 02:06.790
Who do you think?

02:10.400 --> 02:13.320
This company is killing people.

02:13.330 --> 02:17.210
And that's the guy who calls the shots.

02:17.370 --> 02:20.450
"Walter kendrick,ceo."

02:20.470 --> 02:24.220
Ultima natural resources is
destroying the environment.

02:24.240 --> 02:25.770
West virginia.

02:25.790 --> 02:29.360
Acid rain from coal-burning power
plants have pushed mercury levels

02:29.370 --> 02:32.270
to 87 times the national average.

02:32.280 --> 02:34.450
Residents tried to bring a class action.

02:34.460 --> 02:37.020
The judge threw the case out of court.

02:37.030 --> 02:41.290
So,they've had more than 200 lawsuits
filed against them in the past three years?

02:41.310 --> 02:44.920
And they've lost exactly one of them.

02:44.930 --> 02:48.000
They didn't even bother
to appeal. Know why?

02:48.010 --> 02:49.970
It was for $100 million.

02:49.990 --> 02:53.130
That's two days profit for them.

02:53.140 --> 02:55.040
You're right. This is huge.

02:55.050 --> 02:59.950
But what does it have to
do with defending purcell?

02:59.960 --> 03:03.020
I have no idea whether
daniel killed his wife,

03:03.030 --> 03:08.740
but his consulting firm has worked
for unr for more than a decade.

03:09.610 --> 03:12.220
He must know more than he's telling me.

03:12.230 --> 03:18.570
Look,uh... I'm on board,but
you got to tell me something.

03:20.030 --> 03:23.900
You and purcell obviously
have some kind of past.

03:23.910 --> 03:27.700
Is there something
between you,I need to know?

03:29.690 --> 03:32.440
If there was,I'd tell you.

